    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portraits, usually photographs in any format, that depict members of a profession, either singly or in groups. Those depicted are most often wearing clothing associated with that profession, or display tools or other paraphernalia associated with it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
